This directory contains the binary version of the Minimacy Virtual Machine:

- minimacy.exe : windows version
- minimacy : linux without GUI
- minimacyX11GL : linux with X11 and openGL
- minimacyRaspberry64 : raspberry pi 4 with X11 and openGL
- minimacyMac : macos command line without GUI
- minimacyMacX11GL: macos command line with X11 and openGL
